    <abstract>
      <t>This document describes the Vouch By Reference (VBR) protocol.  VBR is a protocol for adding third-party certification to email.  It permits independent third parties to certify the owner of a domain name that is associated with received mail. [STANDARDS-TRACK]
	 </t>
